---
description: Guardrails when editing shared contracts between domains
globs: shared/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Shared contracts

Types, events, and API shapes only — no domain implementation.

## Do

- Keep contracts versioned and explicit (game result, trade proposal, roster snapshot, auth user).
- Update all consumers in the same PR when breaking, or provide a clear migration path.

## Do not

- Put sim math, GM heuristics, React components, or SQL here.
- Let one domain "own" shared silently — call out consumers in the PR.
